data.description: This charming 3-bedroom home with private study in Woodland Park boasts a delightful open floor plan, perfect for entertaining or everyday living. The spacious layout provides captivating views of the fenced backyard and the covered patio, creating a serene atmosphere.  Culinary enthusiasts will delight in the kitchen's beautiful granite countertops, convenient work island, sleek stainless steel appliances, ample storage space, and a breakfast bar for additional seating.  The primary bedroom serves as a peaceful retreat, featuring an en-suite bath with dual sinks, a luxurious deep garden tub, and a separate shower.  Welcome home to this cozy haven, where comfort and style blend effortlessly!
